PrecisAppointment of JoAnne Deneron, of Fort Liard, Northwest Territories, as Vice-Chairperson of the Board of Directors of the Canadian Polar Commission to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years; and appointment of certain persons as members of the Board of Directors of the Canadian Polar Commission to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years. (Michael Kusugak, Rankin Inlet, Northwest Territories; Eva Qmaniq Arreak, Iqaluit, Northwest Territories; and Jon K. Grant, Peterborough, Ontario)
